@node info "About This Issue"

We're still tweaking the AmigaGuide format and looking for satisfactory
solutions to some of the stickier problems.  You'll find that we still
use WDisplay, despite the fact that it is limited to the Workbench
palette.  For this issue, it's less of a problem, since the graphics
aren't as involved as they were last time.

